{"tid":2356024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有大傻仔唔見銀包","createTime":"2021-01-06T13:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T15:48:30.000Z","uid":373610,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"66f16e49794f3cffa0df1d0835acfaa8904ed8a4","tid":2356024,"uid":373610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"嗰個就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概三點幾往城門水塘嘅82號小巴或城門水塘入面唔見咗<br />\n行到&frac14;先發現唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面雖然剩係得幾百 但係銀包同埋啲卡對於我來講好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有心人執到<br />\n就算冇曬啲錢都唔緊要<br />\n如果其他地方見到有人搵失主都可以同我講聲<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjG2Ee1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjG2Ee1.jpg&h=2afa8704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀包示意圖"},{"pid":"5e70827ab06df7b962196eda9ef86e38feb7aa67","tid":2356024,"uid":373610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a14910a042cae5676c3ca03aed25319eddc07ae","tid":2356024,"uid":373610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"冇記錯P牌推唔到post 有冇好心人幫我推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr